  "verses": [
    {
      "n": 1,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Chee nu irr tahs Sem-\nmes Kehnixi/ ko tee Isra-\neta Behrni irr kanwischi/\nun winnu Semmi eemantojschi/\nwinnuſs Jardanas/prett San-\nles Uslehſchanu/ no tahs Arno-\nna Uppes/lihdſtam Ermoza Kal-\nnam/un wiſſam Klaijumam prett\nRihteem.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 2,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Sions tas Amoriteeu Keh-\nnixch/ kas Esbona dshwoja/\nwaldidams no Aroera/ kas pee\ntahs Arnora Uppes Mallasirr/\nun pahr tahs Uppes Widdu/ un\npahr weenu Puſſi no Gileadas/\nun lihds tai Jaboka Uppei/ kas\nto Ammona Behrnu Rohbe-\nscha irr.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 3,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un pahr to Klaijumu/lihds\ntai Kinnerotes Juhrai/ prett\nRihteem/ un lihds tai Klaijuma\nJuhrai/ tai Sahls-Juhrat prett\nRihteem/ us to Zettu lihds Bet-\nJesinotam/ un no Deenas-Wid-\ndus Puſſes us appaſchu ta Pis-\ngas Kalna.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 4,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un ta Rohbescha Oga ta\nKehnixa no Bahsana/ no to Mil-\nsu-Lanschu atliskutcheem/ kas A-\nstarota un Eedrejos dshwoja.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 5,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un waldija pahr to Ermo-\nna Kalnu/ un pahr Salku/ un\npahr wiſſu Bahsanu/ lihds tai\nGesuriteeu/ un Maakatiteeu\nRohbeschai/ un tai weenai Puſ-\nfei Gileadas/ kas Siona ta Keh-\nnixa no Esbona Rohbescha bija.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 6,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Mohsus ta KUNG A\nKalps/ un tee Israeta Behrni\nfawe tohs/ un Mohsus ta KUNG-\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 1,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "GA Kalps dewe to teem Ruhbe-\nnitexeem/ un teem Gaditexeem/\nun tai puſſ Zilti Manaſſus par\neemantojamu Teefu.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 7,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Schee nu irr tahs Sem-\nmes Kehnixi/ ko Josuus un J-\nfraeta Behrni kawe fchaipufs\nJardanas prett Wakkaru/ no\nBaal-Gada eekſch tahs Eeleijas\nLibanus/ lihds tam Ahlaka Kal-\nnam/ kas lihds Setru steepjahs/\nun Josuus dewe to tahm Israe-\nta Ziltim par Zhpaſchunuu pehz\nfawahm Dattahm.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 8,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Kas Kalnds/ un Eeleijas/\nun Klaijumos/ un uhdenaiaa-\nWeetas/ un Tuksnefi/ un prett\nDeenas-Widdu bija/ tee Eetitexi/\ntee Amoriteei/ tee Kananiteei/\nun tee Weresiteei/ tee Gewiteei/\nun tee Jebusiteei.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 9,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Tas Kehnisch no Jerikus-\nweens/ tas Kehnisch no Ajas/\nkas fahns Beteles irr/ weens.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 10,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Tas Kehnisch no Jeru-\nsalemes weens/ tas Kehnisch\nno Gebroza weens.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 11,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Tas Kehnisch no Jar-\nimutes weens/ tas Kehnisch no\nLahkifa weens.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 12,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Tas Kehnisch no Eglo-\nna weens/ tas Kehnisch no Ge-\nsera weens.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 13,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Tas Kehnisch no Debi-\nra weens/ tas Kehnisch no Ge-\ndera weens.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 14,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Tas Kehnisch no Ormas-\nweens/ tas Kehnisch no Arada\nweens.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 15,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Tas Kehnisch no Libnas-\nweens\n"
    }
  ],
  "confidence": "high",
  "notes": ""
}
